INSERT INTO `bbnposts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-39 alignleft\" title=\"img-homepage-kids\" src=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" />\r\n\r\nBumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier nanny agency, located in the heart of vibrant Leslieville. Bumble Bees Nanny Agency specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home–from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers. When using Bumble Bees Nannies we will personally help each client with a personal and customized approach. The result of this is that we only send the right applicants for the job thus saving you time.\r\n\r\nAll caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years’ experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','publish','open','open','','welcome','','','2012-12-03 02:02:37','2012-12-03 02:02:37','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(5,1,'2012-12-03 02:03:46','2012-12-03 02:03:46','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-39 alignleft\" title=\"img-homepage-kids\" src=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" />\n\nBumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier nanny agency, located in the heart of vibrant Leslieville. Bumble Bees Nanny Agency specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home–from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers. When using Bumble Bees Nannies we will personally help each client with a personal and customized approach. The result of this is that we only send the right applicants for the job thus saving you time.\n\nAll caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years’ experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave','','','2012-12-03 02:03:46','2012-12-03 02:03:46','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(6,1,'2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision','','','2012-11-05 02:34:47','2012-11-05 02:34:47','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(7,1,'2012-11-06 03:22:00','2012-11-06 03:22:00','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickies to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-2','','','2012-11-06 03:22:00','2012-11-06 03:22:00','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(8,1,'2012-11-06 03:26:58','2012-11-06 03:26:58','Bumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier boutique nanny agency. Located in the heard of vibrant Leslieville, Bumble Bees Nannies specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home - from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers, Richelle can help you find the right solution for your family. All caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.\r\n\r\n“Hi, my name is Richelle and I am here to help nannies an families find each other. I hope to help families find their perfect nanny efficiently and easily, while helping nannies find a family that they love working for. In my professional career, families have told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.” - Richelle Assenberg , owner of Bumble Bees Nannies\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-3','','','2012-11-06 03:26:58','2012-11-06 03:26:58','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(15,1,'2012-11-06 04:01:16','2012-11-06 04:01:16','','Beaches/Leslieville/Riverdale/ Danforth/Scarborough','','publish','open','open','','beachesleslievilleriverdaledanforthscarborough','','','2012-11-07 01:56:42','2012-11-07 01:56:42','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=15',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(16,1,'2012-11-06 04:01:16','2012-11-06 04:01:16','','Roncesvalles/Ossington/ High Park','','publish','open','open','','roncesvallesossingtonhigh-park','','','2012-11-07 01:56:42','2012-11-07 01:56:42','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=16',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(17,1,'2012-11-06 04:01:16','2012-11-06 04:01:16','','Leaside/Rosedale/Summerhill','','publish','open','open','','leasiderosedalesummerhill','','','2012-11-07 01:56:42','2012-11-07 01:56:42','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=17',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(18,1,'2012-11-06 04:01:16','2012-11-06 04:01:16','','Davisville/Eglinton/Lawrence','','publish','open','open','','davisvilleeglintonlawrence','','','2012-11-07 01:56:43','2012-11-07 01:56:43','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=18',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(21,1,'2012-11-07 01:58:01','2012-11-07 01:58:01','Please select the appropriate job type that suits what you are looking for. If you see a job that you are interested in, please contact us via email with the job number that you are interested in.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"controls\">\r\n<a class=\"btn\" title=\"Full Time\" href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/job-vacancies/full-time/\">Full Time</a><a class=\"btn\" title=\"Part Time\" href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/job-vacancies/part-time/\">Part Time</a><a class=\"btn\" title=\"After School Care\" href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/job-vacancies/after-school-care/\">After School Care</a>\r\n</div>','Job Vacancies','','publish','open','open','','job-vacancies','','','2012-12-06 01:59:19','2012-12-06 01:59:19','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=21',0,'page','',0),(22,1,'2012-11-07 01:57:18','2012-11-07 01:57:18','','test page','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision','','','2012-11-07 01:57:18','2012-11-07 01:57:18','',21,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/21-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(23,1,'2012-11-07 01:58:01','2012-11-07 01:58:01','','test page','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-2','','','2012-11-07 01:58:01','2012-11-07 01:58:01','',21,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/21-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(24,1,'2012-11-07 01:58:30','2012-11-07 01:58:30','','test page','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-3','','','2012-11-07 01:58:30','2012-11-07 01:58:30','',21,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/21-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(25,1,'2012-11-07 02:00:52','2012-11-07 02:00:52','','another page','','trash','open','open','','another-page','','','2012-11-27 04:17:42','2012-11-27 04:17:42','',21,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=25',0,'page','',0),(26,1,'2012-11-07 02:00:48','2012-11-07 02:00:48','','another page','','inherit','open','open','','25-revision','','','2012-11-07 02:00:48','2012-11-07 02:00:48','',25,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/25-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(27,1,'2012-11-07 01:58:41','2012-11-07 01:58:41','','test page','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-4','','','2012-11-07 01:58:41','2012-11-07 01:58:41','',21,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/21-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(28,1,'2012-12-06 01:59:09','2012-12-06 01:59:09','Please select the appropriate job type that suits what you are looking for. If you see a job that you are interested in, please contact us via email with the job number that you are interested in.\n\n<div class=\"controls\">\n<a class=\"btn\" title=\"Full Time\" href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/job-vacancies/full-time/\">Full Time</a><a class=\"btn\" title=\"Part Time\" href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/job-vacancies/part-time/\">Part Time</a><a class=\"btn\" title=\"After School Care\" href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/job-vacancies/after-school-care/\">After School Care</a>\n</div>','Job Vacancies','','inherit','open','open','','21-autosave','','','2012-12-06 01:59:09','2012-12-06 01:59:09','',21,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/21-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(35,1,'2012-11-07 02:27:27','2012-11-07 02:27:27','If you have the right experience, personality and knowledge, we can help you find your perfect job as a LiveIn Nanny, Live-Out Nanny, Mother\'s Helper, After School care or Nanny-share, permanent or temporary, full time or part time. If you are newly qualified or wish to gain further experience, there are many opportunities to explore, such as being a mother\'s helper or even babysitting.\r\n\r\nIf you have the right qualifications and experience, and you successfully complete a series of checks and the interview process, you will be registered as a Bumble Bees Nannies Childcare Professional.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"divider div2\"></div>\r\n\r\n\"Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies. Being a nanny is a fulfilling and professional career choice, working with children on a one to one level, watching them grow up and develop into little adults. You help them through their stages of development and support them in their everyday choices as they get older. I am here to help you find a great family to work with so you also can enjoy these great experiences like I have. Through my seven years of nanny experience I can offer you extra advice and help when deciding a family/job, from interview advice to finding childcare groups in your neighbourhood. I want to help nannies, and share my knowledge and skills - like others have done for me\"\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>','Nannies','','publish','open','open','','nannies','','','2012-12-03 01:29:46','2012-12-03 01:29:46','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=35',0,'page','',0),(36,1,'2012-11-07 02:27:22','2012-11-07 02:27:22','','Nanny','','inherit','open','open','','35-revision','','','2012-11-07 02:27:22','2012-11-07 02:27:22','',35,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/35-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(37,1,'2012-11-07 02:28:10','2012-11-07 02:28:10',' ','','','publish','open','open','','caregivers-2','','','2012-12-06 02:04:54','2012-12-06 02:04:54','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=37',12,'nav_menu_item','',0),(38,1,'2012-11-07 02:53:56','2012-11-07 02:53:56','','Home','','publish','open','open','','home-2','','','2012-12-06 02:04:53','2012-12-06 02:04:53','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=38',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(39,1,'2012-11-07 03:12:51','2012-11-07 03:12:51','','img-homepage-kids','','inherit','open','open','','img-homepage-kids','','','2012-11-07 03:12:51','2012-11-07 03:12:51','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(40,1,'2012-11-06 03:29:16','2012-11-06 03:29:16','Bumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier boutique nanny agency. Located in the heard of vibrant Leslieville, Bumble Bees Nannies specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home - from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers, Richelle can help you find the right solution for your family. All caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.\r\n\r\n“Hi, my name is Richelle and I am here to help nannies an families find each other. I hope to help families find their perfect nanny efficiently and easily, while helping nannies find a family that they love working for. In my professional career, families have told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.”\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-4','','','2012-11-06 03:29:16','2012-11-06 03:29:16','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(41,1,'2012-11-07 03:13:29','2012-11-07 03:13:29','<a href=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-39\" title=\"img-homepage-kids\" src=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" /></a>Bumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier boutique nanny agency. Located in the heard of vibrant Leslieville, Bumble Bees Nannies specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home - from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers, Richelle can help you find the right solution for your family. All caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.\r\n\r\n“Hi, my name is Richelle and I am here to help nannies an families find each other. I hope to help families find their perfect nanny efficiently and easily, while helping nannies find a family that they love working for. In my professional career, families have told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.”\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-5','','','2012-11-07 03:13:29','2012-11-07 03:13:29','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(42,1,'2012-11-07 03:15:37','2012-11-07 03:15:37','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-39 alignleft\" title=\"img-homepage-kids\" src=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" />Bumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier boutique nanny agency. Located in the heard of vibrant Leslieville, Bumble Bees Nannies specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home - from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers, Richelle can help you find the right solution for your family. All caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.\r\n\r\n“Hi, my name is Richelle and I am here to help nannies an families find each other. I hope to help families find their perfect nanny efficiently and easily, while helping nannies find a family that they love working for. In my professional career, families have told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.”\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-6','','','2012-11-07 03:15:37','2012-11-07 03:15:37','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/2-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(43,1,'2012-11-11 17:02:51','2012-11-11 17:02:51','Here is some text to represent the first blog post on the site.\r\n\r\nGreat isn\'t it? Awesome.','First Blog Post','','publish','open','open','','first-blog-post','','','2012-11-11 17:02:51','2012-11-11 17:02:51','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=43',0,'post','',0),(44,1,'2012-11-11 17:02:32','2012-11-11 17:02:32','','First Blog Post','','inherit','open','open','','43-revision','','','2012-11-11 17:02:32','2012-11-11 17:02:32','',43,'http://localhost/bumblebees/2012/11/43-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(45,1,'2012-11-11 17:05:27','2012-11-11 17:05:27','Here is another posting so we have a bunch to display\r\n\r\nLike it?','The Second posting!','','publish','open','open','','the-second-posting','','','2012-11-11 17:05:27','2012-11-11 17:05:27','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=45',0,'post','',0),(46,1,'2012-11-11 17:05:14','2012-11-11 17:05:14','','The Second posting!','','inherit','open','open','','45-revision','','','2012-11-11 17:05:14','2012-11-11 17:05:14','',45,'http://localhost/bumblebees/blog/45-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(47,1,'2012-11-11 17:05:44','2012-11-11 17:05:44','...For good measure.\r\n\r\nWe have a last posting for posterity.','One more','','publish','open','open','','one-more','','','2012-11-11 17:39:58','2012-11-11 17:39:58','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=47',0,'post','',0),(48,1,'2012-11-11 17:05:33','2012-11-11 17:05:33','','One more','','inherit','open','open','','47-revision','','','2012-11-11 17:05:33','2012-11-11 17:05:33','',47,'http://localhost/bumblebees/blog/47-revision/',0,'revision','',0)