yment relationship, it is not because of unreasonable demands being made by you or because there has been a change in the job description, hours, pay or job location originally agreed to between you and the nanny.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n	<li>THIRD PARTY INTRODUCTION - I/We agree to notify Bumble Bees immediately, either verbally or in writing, if a nanny candidate presented by Bumble Bees has previously been introduced to me/us by a third party. Otherwise, I/we acknowledge and agree that Bumble Bees will be considered to have introduced the nanny candidate to me/us and the relevant Fee shall be payable to Bumble Bees.</li>\n	<li>I/WE ARE THE EMPLOYER - I/We understand that I/we will be the employer of the selected nanny candidate that I/we will be responsible for entering into an employment contract with the nanny, paying all wages and benefits (if any)to the nanny, making all relevant employment deductions and remittances to the relevant government department, and providing all employment-related documentation to the nanny, as required by and in accordance with all employment and income tax laws in effect from time to time in the province of Ontario.</li>\n	<li>SUITABILITY AND REFERENCES – I/We understand that while Bumble Bees endeavours to ensure the suitability of the nanny candidates provided, the final decision to employ a nanny candidate is my/our responsibility and Bumble Bees does not warrant the suitability, honesty, capability or character of any nanny candidate introduced to me/us. Accordingly, I/we understand that I/we must:\n<ol type=\"a\">\n	<li>(a) Satisfy myself/ourselves as to the overall suitability of the nanny for my/our family;</li>\n	<li>(b) Check the references provided by a nanny candidate prior to making an offer of employment; and</li>\n	<li>(c) Verify the identification, work status, qualifications, and any other required criteria of the nanny candidate as would a prudent employer.</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n	<li>INSURANCE - I/We will ensure that I/we have adequate insurance coverage for any possible losses sustained as a result of the employment of a child care worker in my/our home.</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n9. ADDITIONAL ADVICE MAY BE NECESSARY - While Bumble Bees offers assistance in setting up the employment relationship with any nanny candidate, I/we understand that we are ultimately responsible as employers, and will seek any such additional legal, accounting, immigration or other advice as required.\n\n10. CONFIDENTIALITY - I/We agree to keep all information concerning nanny candidates confidential. I/We agree not to disclose any information concerning the nanny candidates provided by Bumble Bees to third parties without the express written consent of Bumble Bees. I/We acknowledge and agree that should unauthorized disclosure of such information be made to a third party resulting in the employment of a nanny candidate first introduced to me by Bumble Bees, that I may responsible to Bumble Bees for any and all fees owing.\n\n11. LIABILITY – I/We agree that Bumble Bees will not be held liable for any claim by me/us for any loss or damage which may be incurred by us, howsoever caused, as a result of the introduction to or employment by me/us of any nanny candidate, or due the failure of Bumble Bees to introduce any nanny candidate to me/us.\n\n12. ACCEPTANCE - By signing below I/we acknowledge having read, understood and agree to the above terms and conditions.','Terms & Conditions','','inherit','open','open','','324-revision','','','2012-12-03 01:43:24','2012-12-03 01:43:24','',324,'http://localhost/bumblebees/blog/324-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(326,1,'2012-12-03 01:44:59','2012-12-03 01:44:59',' ','','','publish','open','open','','326','','','2012-12-03 01:44:59','2012-12-03 01:44:59','',0,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=326',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(327,1,'2012-12-03 01:44:04','2012-12-03 01:44:04','BUMBLE BEES NANNIES INC.\r\nCLIENT AGREEMENT\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li> OUR CONTRACT - Bumble Bees Nannies Inc. (“B