ave told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.”\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-8','','','2012-12-03 02:01:09','2012-12-03 02:01:09','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/blog/2-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0),(338,1,'2012-12-03 02:01:26','2012-12-03 02:01:26','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-39 alignleft\" title=\"img-homepage-kids\" src=\"http://localhost/bumblebees/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/img-homepage-kids.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" />Bumble Bees Nannies is Toronto’s premier boutique nanny agency. Located in the heard of vibrant Leslieville, Bumble Bees Nannies specializes in placing the right childcare professional in the right home - from qualified Nannies, Nanny-Shares and experienced After-School Caregivers, Richelle can help you find the right solution for your family. All caregivers will have an Early Childhood qualification and/or many years experience, background and reference checks, and current CPR and First Aid certifications.\r\n\r\n“Hi, my name is Richelle and I am here to help nannies an families find each other. I hope to help families find their perfect nanny efficiently and easily, while helping nannies find a family that they love working for. In my professional career, families have told me the difficulties they faced finding a trustworthy and responsible nanny, a nanny that shared their philosophy on childcare. While caring for your children, a nanny also shares your home - it’s imperative that you are able to trust and partner with your nanny in keeing your children safe and secure. My goal in operating Bumble Bees Nannies is to find that perfect relationship for family and nanny.”\r\n\r\n- <strong>Richelle Assenberg</strong>, owner of <strong>Bumble Bees Nannies</strong>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Welcome to Bumble Bees Nannies','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-9','','','2012-12-03 02:01:26','2012-12-03 02:01:26','',2,'http://localhost/bumblebees/blog/2-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(339,1,'2012-12-03 02:06:53','2012-12-03 02:06:53','“After interviewing multiple nannies and not finding the right fit for our family we decided to give Bumble Bee Nannies a try. Richelle was immediately helpful and warm and took note of our special needs. All her applicants were wonderful, a step up from the other nannies we had interviewed. Ultimately, we have been extremely happy with our lovely nanny and our son definitely gives her a high five”\r\n- <strong>J.O- Mother from Leslieville</strong>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n“Bumble Bees Nannies were very knowledgeable and helpful when it came to finding someone for our nanny share position. Being a first-time parent, I was intimidated by the prospect of having to find a nanny to care for my son and my friend\'s daughter. Not only did they answer our many questions, but they were also able to find us a nanny that is a truly wonderful fit with both families. Our children enjoy spending time with her and we have peace of mind knowing that they are getting quality care every day. Thank you Bumble Bees Nannies!”\r\n- <strong>J.H Mother from East Toronto</strong>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n“Bumble Bees Nannies took the daunting task of finding the right childcare and made it simple! Richelle was such a tremendous help to my friend and I who were searching for a nanny to do a share with. We simply communicated what we were looking for and Richelle presented us with 3 women to interview and all were wonderful. We now have a fantastic nanny who is loving and interactive with our children and the kids adore her! A great service for busy parents who want the best for their family”\r\n- <strong>S.P Toronto</strong>\r\n\r\n<hr>\r\n\r\n“Great Nanny Agency! The service that we received from Richelle at Bumble Bees Nannies was unlike any other nanny agency that we have dealt with in Toronto. Previous agencies had just sent us nanny after nanny which we had to interview to find out that they were not fit with our family. Bumble Bees Nannies listened to our needs as a family and worked to find us the right nanny from the start. Richelle only had to send us 2 nannies to interview before we found the perfect match and that is all down to her hard work in the background. This saved us time and money. We have recommended using Bumble Bees Nannies to all of our friends”\r\n- <strong>Father from East Toronto</strong>','Testimonials From Parents','','publish','open','open','','from-parents','','','2012-12-06 02:00:54','2012-12-06 02:00:54','',349,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?page_id=339',0,'page','',0),(340,1,'2012-12-03 02:05:55','2012-12-03 02:05:55','“After interviewing multiple nannies and not finding the right fit for our family we decided to give Bumble Bee Nannies a try. Richelle was immediately helpful and warm and took note of our special needs. All her applicants were wonderful, a step up from the other nannies we had interviewed. Ultimately, we have been extremely happy with our lovely nanny and our son definitely gives her a high five” J.O- Mother from Leslieville\n“Bumble Bees Nannies were very knowledgeable and helpful when it came to finding someone for our nanny share position. Being a first-time parent, I was intimidated by the prospect of having to find a nanny to care for my son and my friend\'s daughter. Not only did they answer our many questions, but they were also able to find us a nanny that is a truly wonderful fit with both families. Our children enjoy spending time with her and we have peace of mind knowing that they are getting quality care every day. Thank you Bumble Bees Nannies!” J.H Mother from East Toronto\n“Bumble Bees Nannies took the daunting task of finding the right childcare and made it simple! Richelle was such a tremendous help to my friend and I who were searching for a nanny to do a share with. We simply communicated what we were looking for and Richelle presented us with 3 women to interview and all were wonderful. We now have a fantastic nanny who is loving and interactive with our children and the kids adore her! A great service for busy parents who want the best for their family” S.P Toronto\n“Great Nanny Agency! The service that we received from Richelle at Bumble Bees Nannies was unlike any other nanny agency that we have dealt with in Toronto. Previous agencies had just sent us nanny after nanny which we had to interview to find out that they were not fit with our family. Bumble Bees Nannies listened to our needs as a family and worked to find us the right nanny from the start. Richelle only had to send us 2 nannies to interview before we found the perfect match and that is all down to her hard work in the background. This saved us time and money. We have recommended using Bumble Bees Nannies to all of our friends” Father from East Toronto','Testimonials From Parents','','inherit','open','open','','339-revision','','','2012-12-03 02:05:55','2012-12-03 02:05:55','',339,'http://localhost/bumblebees/blog/339-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(342,1,'2012-12-03 02:07:42','2012-12-03 02:07:42','','From Parents','','publish','open','open','','from-parents','','','2012-12-06 02:04:55','2012-12-06 02:04:55','',349,'http://localhost/bumblebees/?p=342',25,'nav_menu_item','',0),(343,1,'2012-12-03 02:09:44','2012-12-03 02:09:44','Quality Excellent\r\n\r\nI\'m so pleased with the experience I had with Richelle. She was in contact with me throughout the experience and she matched me with a family that matched me perfectly. I have never been happier with my work. Richelle really wo